EventDescription: GDG DevFests are large scale community-run events that can offer speaker sessions across Google product areas, all-day hack-a-thons or both. It is a platform for developers, entrepreneurs and tech enthusiasts to come together and get inspired by the latest technologies. Each GDG DevFest will be inspired by and uniquely tailored to the needs of the developer community that hosts it. Know more about Keynotes and Hackathon
